INSERT INTO `cms_config` VALUES ('about', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.4em; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">增长，一直是企业关心的话题，在流量红利逐渐消失、获客成本越来越高的现在，如何低成本获客是企业要优先思考的，其中裂变不失为一种低投入、高回报的增长用户的方式。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<figure style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.4em; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-size=\"normal\"><img class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;\" src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-748eaca4da08c76619b13eadfb1f1dba_1440w.jpg\" width=\"1080\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"715\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-748eaca4da08c76619b13eadfb1f1dba_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-748eaca4da08c76619b13eadfb1f1dba_b.jpg\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">图源：来自Pexels</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">纵观一些在较短时间内可以增长大量用户的品牌：无论是时不时让你帮忙砍一刀的拼多多，还是用短短18个月就上市的瑞幸咖啡，无一例外的，它们通过一些营销手段让用户自己产生分享欲主动分享从而达到裂变的目的。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">它们都有一个特点，就是或多或少的在微信这个平台上发力进行裂变，瑞幸咖啡在微信上有自己的小程序，而拼多多更不用说，它就是以微信作为跳板，直接把链接分享给微信好友裂变用户。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">为什么它们甚至越来越多的品牌开始通过微信平台进行裂变？</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">原因有三，第一，微信的用户基数大，微信月活已超12亿，相比其他平台用户数量上更具优势。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第二，微信的功能愈发强大，原有的微信生态被划分为四大流量触点：公众号、小程序、社群、个人号，我们可以通多这四点多次触达客户，随着企业微信、视频号、微信直播加入流量触点大家庭，会衍生出很多新的更多的裂变方法，有非常大的增长潜力和空间。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第三，微信可以更精准的接触到达目标用户，每个人的微信号都是一个巨大的私域流量池，而你现有用户的朋友圈，还有更多的潜在客户。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">所以，微信是一个流量巨大且易触达到用户的平台，很容易就实现裂变。可以说在微信这个平台上，想要裂变增长客户有很多打法，今天我们就来推荐一本基于微信的裂变增长指南——<span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">《裂变增长秘籍》</span>。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">其作者小裂变团队花费了大量的时间和精力编写出此书，这本书是<span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">基于微信大生态</span>，围绕着<span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">裂变获客、留存促活、销售变现、客户管理</span>四大板块展开讲述，旨在帮助更多人学会裂变增长，树立用户增长的全局观，对老板来说，是一本不可多得的工具书。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<figure style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-size=\"normal\"><img class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;\" src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-47768879834af0e5757d5cb4e7c0523e_1440w.jpg\" width=\"1080\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"719\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-47768879834af0e5757d5cb4e7c0523e_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-47768879834af0e5757d5cb4e7c0523e_b.jpg\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">图源：来自小裂变官方公众号</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">此书200余页，共分为五大章节，如果阅读这本书，你将会学到以下内容：</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第一章——学习如何调动微信全领域流量，多点触达并获取新用户，包括：公众号、小程序、社群裂变、个人号裂变、企业微信裂变等方面的方法剖析和经典案例拆解；</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第二章——学习如何做到用户留存与促活的方法；</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第三章——学习要拥抱运营销售化大趋势，善用线上分销工具，比如分销、拼团、直播等。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第四章——学习如何从私域流量到私域留存，科学管理存量客户；</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">第五章——真实裂变增长案例的讲解与分析。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<figure style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-size=\"normal\"><img class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;\" src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5707b96bb8138c59144ccca87df19be0_1440w.jpg\" width=\"750\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"933\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5707b96bb8138c59144ccca87df19be0_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5707b96bb8138c59144ccca87df19be0_b.jpg\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">图源：来自小裂变官方公众号</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">以下是我摘录的书中精彩语录，希望可以给大家提供裂变增长相关知识点的同时还可以给大家一些思考：</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">什么是好的增长</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">我一直在思考“增长”这个问题。什么是好的增长？是纯粹的用户量暴涨吗，是销售额的短期增长吗？是，但也不完全对等。我理解的好的增长是：在用户量不断增长的过程中，让用户持续高频地体验、消费你的产品和服务。</p>');
