INSERT INTO `cms_notice` VALUES (7, '柚枝集资讯类小程序即将发售', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.4em; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">今天开始正式学习微信小程序，小程序有多火我也不说了，作为前端开发者，小程序也是必备技能。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">由于我有vue的开发经验，已经多年的html+css开发经验，所以相对来说学习比较简单，看了一下b站的视频，就开始尝试开发起来，此小程序是以本网站即 <a class=\" wrap external\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid #808080;\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.shuanghei.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"1043\">shuanghei.com</a>的手机版为原型来开发的，也算是小程序的入门项目，个人博客。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">此系列文章，仅仅是记录下本人开发小程序的一些过程和心得，并非教学类文章，我会把我开发小程序的点点滴滴的过程，都一一记录下来，与大家分享。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px calc(1.27273em); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.5; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; clear: left; color: #121212; background-color: #ffffff;\">一，创建项目</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">去官网申请appid，然后新建项目填入appid，不要勾选云开发，小程序会默认生成几个文件夹。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<figure style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.4em; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-size=\"normal\"><img class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;\" src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4333f9ee1d2501766a5813614ee104ed_1440w.jpg\" width=\"793\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"793\" data-rawheight=\"559\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4333f9ee1d2501766a5813614ee104ed_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4333f9ee1d2501766a5813614ee104ed_b.jpg\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">把app.js和app.wxss里面的内容清空，然后删除pages下的index文件夹，重新新建index文件夹，这样就是一个最干净的初始项目。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: calc(1.90909em) 0px calc(1.27273em); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.5; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; clear: left; color: #121212; background-color: #ffffff;\">二，全局设置</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">打开app.json，进行简单的全局设置，backgroundTextStyle和navigationBarTextStyle是全局的背景色，只能是light和white，navigationBarTitleText是小程序的标题，我就用公众号一样的名字吧。</p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: calc(0.888889em); font-size: 0.9em; word-break: initial; overflow-wrap: initial; overflow: auto; background: #f6f6f6; border-radius: 4px;\"><code class=\"language-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 0px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Andale Mono\', \'lucida console\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: inherit;\">\"window\": {\r\n        \"backgroundTextStyle\": \"light\",\r\n        \"navigationBarBackgroundColor\": \"#000\",\r\n        \"navigationBarTitleText\": \"双黑in上海\",\r\n        \"navigationBarTextStyle\": \"white\"\r\n  },</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">pages对象里，新建3个page，主要是底部导航对应的page。</p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: calc(0.888889em); font-size: 0.9em; word-break: initial; overflow-wrap: initial; overflow: auto; background: #f6f6f6; border-radius: 4px;\"><code class=\"language-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 0px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Andale Mono\', \'lucida console\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: inherit;\">\"pages\": [\r\n        \"pages/index/index\",\r\n        \"pages/logs/logs\",\r\n        \"pages/blog/blog\",\r\n        \"pages/about/about\"\r\n  ],</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">可以看到，创建完这三个页面后，左侧pages文件夹里，会自动生成这三个page。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<figure style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-size=\"normal\"><img class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;\" src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3855403314d2cf9112a76937ab7a3aa9_1440w.jpg\" width=\"599\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"599\" data-rawheight=\"327\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3855403314d2cf9112a76937ab7a3aa9_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3855403314d2cf9112a76937ab7a3aa9_b.jpg\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: calc(1.90909em) 0px calc(1.27273em); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.5; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; clear: left; color: #121212; background-color: #ffffff;\">三，创建导航</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">接下去，创建底部导航，目前就先创建，首页、博客、关于三个页面吧，以后可以根据项目再补充。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">这里的pagePath必须在之前的pages对象中存在，否则会报错。</p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: calc(0.888889em); font-size: 0.9em; word-break: initial; overflow-wrap: initial; overflow: auto; background: #f6f6f6; border-radius: 4px;\"><code class=\"language-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 0px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Andale Mono\', \'lucida console\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: inherit;\">\"tabBar\": {\r\n    \"selectedColor\":\"#D81E06\",\r\n    \"list\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"pagePath\": \"pages/index/index\",\r\n        \"text\": \"首页\",\r\n        \"iconPath\":\"/images/home.png\",\r\n        \"selectedIconPath\":\"/images/home-h.png\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"pagePath\": \"pages/blog/blog\",\r\n        \"text\": \"博客\",\r\n        \"iconPath\":\"/images/blog.png\",\r\n        \"selectedIconPath\":\"/images/blog-h.png\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"pagePath\": \"pages/about/about\",\r\n        \"text\": \"关于\",\r\n        \"iconPath\":\"/images/about.png\",\r\n        \"selectedIconPath\":\"/images/about-h.png\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  },</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">iconPath和selectedIconPath分别是未选中和选中状态下的icon，selectedColor选中状态下的文字颜色建议和selectedIconPath所指定的icon的图便一样。至于icon可以去<a class=\" external\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid #808080;\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.iconfont.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"1043\"><span class=\"invisible\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; font-family: a; color: transparent; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent;\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">iconfont.cn/</span></a>免费下载。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">在线就可以编辑不同的颜色的png图片，非常方便，如下图：</p>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<figure style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-size=\"normal\"><img class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;\" src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d1f208d061a594bbacc00f1ad0bbf59_1440w.jpg\" width=\"911\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"911\" data-rawheight=\"624\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2d1f208d061a594bbacc00f1ad0bbf59_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2d1f208d061a594bbacc00f1ad0bbf59_b.jpg\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\" /></figure>\r\n<p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\" style=\"margin: -0.8em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.4em 0px; color: #121212; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">最后，然后预览一下，看看效果，有那么点感觉了？</p>', 1, 0, '2021-09-15 19:12:11', NULL, '2021-09-16 12:04:00');
COMMIT;

