-16323696977423=\"rgb(163, 163, 163)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(51, 51, 51)\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(163, 163, 163)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(51, 51, 51)\">&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n</section>\r\n</section>\r\n</section>\r\n<p class=\"js_darkmode__18\" style=\"margin: 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" data-style=\"margin: 0px 0em; text-align: left; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\">很多人有个问题，凭啥同样流量同样点击同样数据，他10块我1块？</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"js_darkmode__19\" style=\"margin: 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" data-style=\"margin: 0px 0em; text-align: left; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" />1.用户城市分类：你知道不同城市的用户，点击你的广告，收取的费用是不一样的吗？就是地域区别：一类城市千次曝光二类城市千次曝光100，三类城市千次曝光50。</p>\r\n<p class=\"js_darkmode__20\" style=\"margin: 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" data-style=\"margin: 0px 0em; text-align: left; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" />2.用户行为习惯：大家知道广告费用是不同的，那么游戏广告比普通广告贵。但是广告是大数据随机的，会根据用户的行为习惯去优化，所以一个爱玩游戏的人点击你的广告，你赚的就多，相反一个不爱花钱多人，点你广告钱就少。</p>\r\n<p class=\"js_darkmode__21\" style=\"margin: 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" data-style=\"margin: 0px 0em; text-align: left; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" />3.用户操作方式：最后，同样一个广告，同样的微信，那么怎样会增加收入呢？很简单，广告费按步骤收取，第一展示，用户看了就给钱，第二点击，点了就给钱，第三下载，下载就给钱，第四试玩，试玩就给钱。你做到哪一步，钱就赚到哪一步。</p>\r\n<p class=\"js_darkmode__22\" style=\"margin: 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-darkmode-color-16323696977423=\"rgb(141, 141, 141)\" data-darkmode-original-color-16323696977423=\"#fff|rgb(89, 89, 89)\" data-style=\"margin: 0px 0em; text-align: left; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;\">&nbsp;</p>', 24, 0, 0, 73, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-19 19:23:48', '2021-09-25 18:08:42');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (10, 'IPHONE“十三香”到底香不香', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/d8e7a7903eada86216f738706b36c9ba.jpg', '[]', '<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">iPhone 13系列在苹果官网和各大电商平台开启预购，仅仅几分钟均被「秒光」，苹果官网一时也陷入瘫痪状况。新配色中，猛男粉不到3分钟就被一抢而空，果然还是十三香！</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_mediaWrap_213jB \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; display: flex; margin-top: 36px; font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"index-module_contentImg_JmmC0\" style=\"display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 599px;\"><img src=\"https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/tinymce/images/12bce0e8480c4faa974a74c3a27891f3614ef1bbb006d.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1079\" height=\"1439\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 36px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">下面具体来看：</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">9月17日晚间，苹果iPhone 13系列智能手机开始在苹果官网和各大电商平台开启预售。预售开始后不久，各平台均遭遇&ldquo;秒没&rdquo;状况，苹果官网也出现页面卡顿等状况。iPhone 13系列手机开启预售后几分钟，苹果官方商店显示正在更新。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">苹果官网系统崩溃，不少网友表示：付款的时候卡掉了，订单也完全点不进去，想重新下单，结果又没货了。硬生生刷新到订单过期也没付上款。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">在京东平台，当iPhone 13系列开启预售后也被&ldquo;秒光&rdquo;。此前，京东对外表示，当iPhone 13发布后，京东页面上线后仅1小时，iPhone 13系列预约人数已突破20万。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">天猫、拼多多也在30分钟内纷纷售空。官网显示，iPhone 13的发货时间预计7-10个工作日，iPhone 13 Pro预计3-4周发货。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">目前为止，所有型号都已经恢复正常购买，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">但是发货时间显示&ldquo;购买后47天之内&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">事实上，iPhone 13正式发布后，粉色款立即就冲上热搜，不少网友也调侃，库克真是太了解用户的喜好。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">另外，今年苹果新推出的1TB容量的&ldquo;顶配版本&rdquo;也很早就被抢光，可见消费者对于大容量的追求。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">值得注意的是，今年苹果更改了&ldquo;到店取货&rdquo;的购买流程，以往消费者只需登录账户选择好机型和门店后，输入个人信息即可完成取货预约。但今年苹果则要求先付款再取货，对于本身就在拼手速的消费者来说，增加了录入付款信息和账单信息的步骤，抢购流程变长。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">从这次预售的激烈程度来看，和去年iPhone 12以及iPhone 12 Pro更受欢迎，尤其是iPhone 12 Pro一机难求不同，今年最先卖光的iPhone 13 Pro系列两款产品，而iPhone 12和iPhone 12 mini其实还是比较容易购买的，尤其是iPhone 12 mini，很长一段时间有货的。其实这个现象也可以理解，iPhone 13主要升级点在于影像，这个东西对于普通用户来说感知并不强，相反iPhone 13 Pro系列升级了高刷新率、影像等等，尤其是前者我觉得在日常使用当中差距还是非常明显的。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">不过没有买到的果粉朋友也无需着急，根据之前的经验，官网排单时间很长，但其他平台多数会比官网更快实现现货，甚至往年还出现了官网未发货，有的平台已经降价的情况，所以除非你有24期免息的需求，否则可以去其他电商平台购买。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_mediaWrap_213jB \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; display: flex; margin-top: 36px; font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"index-module_contentImg_JmmC0\" style=\"display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 599px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 36px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">此外呢，今天明美无限还要顺便一提的是，在等待 iPhone 13 系列到货的时候，外媒已经提前预订了所有适用于新款 iPhone 的硅胶保护套。本次苹果提供了灰粉色、雀羽蓝色、金盏花色、苜蓿草色、深邃蓝、柚粉色、午夜色、红色八种颜色，售价为 399 元。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">在iPhone 12 系列中，一个保护壳的尺寸既适合 iPhone 12，也适合 iPhone 12 Pro。不过在 iPhone 13 阵容中，这种情况不再存在。尽管 iPhone 13 和 iPhone 13 Pro 具有相同的物理尺寸，但摄像头的凸起却有很大的不同。iPhone 13 Pro 的摄像头凸起要大得多。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">正因为如此，iPhone 12 的保护壳将不适合 iPhone 13 或 iPhone 13 Pro。此外，iPhone 13 的保护壳将不适合 iPhone 13 Pro。为 iPhone 13 Pro 设计的外壳将适合 iPhone 13，但在摄像头凸起周围会有很多多余的空间。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">除此之外呢，今天明美无限还要值得一提的是，据悉此次苹果包装盒有所调整。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">据媒体消息，iPhone 13包装盒采用纸质撕拉式设计，仅需轻轻一拉即可打开。专业人士表示：保证了盒子在运输过程中不会意外打开，也起到了防篡改密封的作用。此前苹果表示，iPhone 13包装盒将去掉外层塑料包装，从而减少包装材料。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">苹果官方表示：我们决定不再使用塑料膜包覆iPhone 13和 iPhone 13 Pro的包装盒，从而少用塑料达600吨。另外，苹果已建成的总装工厂现在也都实现了废弃物零填埋。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">为什么这次这么火？</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">在中国市场，苹果对iPhone 13系列的定价则又有一些优惠，与iPhone 12系列同容量相比，有300-800元的降价。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">其中，iPhone 13 mini起步容量为128GB，售价5199元，基本上杀入5000元档。与国产高端机形成了直接的价格竞争。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">&ldquo;加量不加价&rdquo;　</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">创新不足性价比来补</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">iPhone 13系列主要亮点可以概括为：性能提升，刘海缩小，续航提高。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-heigh