round-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">512GB 版本售价：8399 元</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">众多业内人士对iPhone的最新定价感到意外，因为业内领先的芯片制造商台积电最近上调了价格。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">市场人士认为，苹果iPhone 13系列产品降价，可能会导致华为、小米、vivo、OPPO等本土市场份额下滑。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">库克此次带来的苹果新品，说得好听一些是常规升级，说得难听一点就是毫无创意，没有大刀阔斧的突破性改变。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">但是和上一代相比更低的价格和精准到令人拍案叫绝的功能升级，不少网友惊呼苹果刀法精湛，从这么抢手的程度看，确实是&ldquo;十三香&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">去年上半年，华为高端手机的市场份额达44.1%，苹果为44%，但在眼下的整体行业背景下，苹果注定将要夺取中国高端手机市场的大部分份额，分析师预测iPhone的超级周期会因此延长。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">分析预测，全球拥有3年以上老机型并有升级需求的用户高达2.5亿，业内人士分析，预计中国市场至少有7000万苹果老用户需要更新换代。Strategy Analytics则认为，2021年iPhone 13系列全球出货量将超过9000万部。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">去年iPhone 12系列的首批出货量为7200万台。今年首批备货量或达到1亿台，后续苹果仍可能加大A15芯片订单量。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">国内高端手机市场或将再次被苹果&ldquo;统治&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_mediaWrap_213jB \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; display: flex; margin-top: 36px; font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"index-module_contentImg_JmmC0\" style=\"display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 599px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 36px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\">明美无限说到最后</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\" data-from-paste=\"1\" data-diagnose-id=\"aa9b5d1dd91713da6b481dbd01ea5e9e\">如果大家在iPhone 12和iPhone 13之间犹豫不决的话，建议是买新款iPhone 13得，128GB版价格就贵了几百块。就在大家吹捧iPhone 13是真香机的时候，外媒扯下苹果&ldquo;遮羞布&rdquo;，iPhone 13得GPU核心数减少了一个，便宜没好货？不过眼前有一个问题，如果大家非5G苹果手机不选的话，当下性价比较高的仍是这台iPhone 13，其它机型暂不建议考虑，有预算的建议买Pro版本，你们认为这一代产品有诚意吗？</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"index-module_textWrap_3ygOc \" style=\"max-width: 100%; overflow-x: visible; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; margin-top: 22px; font-family: arial; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-y: auto; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\" data-from-paste=\"1\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;\" data-from-paste=\"1\" data-diagnose-id=\"b7b670c1c76dfe254688079eab61b0b0\">当然了，不着急入手的小伙伴也可以等过一段时间再入手，毕竟再过两个月就是双11了。到时候电商平台的新iPhone价格可能会低个几百块，那时候入手应该是最优惠的。不过，早买早享受不是吗？</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 24, 0, 1, 57, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 17:54:18', '2021-09-25 18:09:43');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (11, '史诗级更新！微信 PC 端支持自动登录，无需手机确认', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/fcd8fecc05d3793deb9328a31fe706c5.jpeg', '[]', '<div class=\"whale_news_detail-content\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"whale_news_index-inner\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto 60px; width: 1200px;\">\r\n<div class=\"whale_news_detail-article-content flex\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: flex;\">\r\n<article class=\"whale_news-detail-content-article l\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; float: left; width: 895px;\">\r\n<div id=\"articleContent\" class=\"whale_news-detail-content-content forum-viewthread-article-box imgAltshow\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px; margin: 0px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; width: 835px; box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">最近，微信为微信 Windows 客户端添加了一项新功能，在登录 PC 端微信之后，在手机端可选择【自动登录该设备】，下次再打开就不需要在手机上确认登录了，当然你也可以在 PC 客户端中进行设置。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/24/63584202109240944346036.jpeg\" alt=\"图源网络\" /></p>\r\n<p>图源网络</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">值得注意的是，目前的微信只支持两个设备登录，也就是说，当你的 PC 客户端登录时，平板端是无法登录的。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2