INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (12, 'AirPods Pro/Max 的查找功能缺席：推迟到今年秋季晚些时候', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/1197ff5745e8f2e8ff3ca389159177b7.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">目前，iOS 15 已经正式向用户推送，在此前发布会中曾提到的&nbsp;<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">AirPods Pro/Max 并未出现在正式版中。</span><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"https://feng-bbs-att-1255531212.image.myqcloud.com/2021/09/20/113341vrbs6j6scpdbbgbs.jpg?imageMogr2/format/jpg/interlace/0/quality/100\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">据悉，这项功能已经被苹果延期推进，苹果表示</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">查找网络支持推迟到今年秋天晚些时候。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">查找功能，假如丢失了 AirPods Pro 或 AirPods Max，耳机将会向手机发出最后遗落的位置。失主进入耳机蓝牙范围内就可以通过播放声音准确找到耳机位置。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">同时，遗落的&nbsp;AirPods Pro 也会在附近拥有苹果设备的人经过时，<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">将耳机的大致位置转发给你。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">与此同时，还有几项功能也要到今年晚些时候，比如 SharePlay、钱包应用驾照等等。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">尾巴们，你们冲 iOS 15 正式版了吗？小编已经更新了呢，说说你最喜欢的新功能呗~~</p>', 24, 1, 1, 73, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 1, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:04:13', '2021-09-25 18:04:22');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (13, 'JBL 发布一系列音频新品，Flip 6 蓝牙音箱支持 IP67 防尘防水', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/01d6d9e3c2a3218f4e0834645001f84b.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">最近，JBL 更新了旗下的 Flip 蓝牙音箱系列，推出 Flip 6，相较于上一代 Flip 5 只支持 IPX7 防水，Flip 6 升级为支持 IP67 防尘防水等级。</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/9db23202109031031126426.jpeg\" alt=\"JBL Flip 6\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">JBL Flip 6</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">此外，Flip 6 的蓝牙版本也从 4.2 提升到了 5.1，并采用了全新设计的 JBL 标志。</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">电池续航保持不变，约为 12 小时。12 月在美国上市，零售价为 129.95 美元（约 839.48 元人民币），高于 Flip 5 目前 119.95 美元（约 774.88 元人民币）的价格。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">另外，JBL 还发布了一系列新的音频产品，比如 Partybox 110 和 710，这两款大体积音箱支持吉他和麦克风输入，可用于即兴音乐创作，其零售价分别为 399.95 美元（约 2583.68 元人民币）和 799.95 美元（约 5167.68 元人民币）。</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/c88fc20210903103252721.jpeg\" alt=\"JBL Partybox 110\" /> JBL Partybox 110</figure>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/27cf2202109031032574409.jpeg\" alt=\"JBL Partybox 710\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">JBL Partybox 710</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">JBL 还推出了一系列耳机，有 99.95 美元的 Quantum 350 游戏耳机（本月上市）；</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/3f7fe202109031034207489.jpeg\" alt=\"Quantum 350\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">Quantum 350</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">真无线耳机 Reflect Flow Pro（179.95 美元，11 月上市）；</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/d9c54202109031034481621.jpeg\" alt=\"Reflect Flow Pro\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">Reflect Flow Pro</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tune 230NC 和 Tune 130NC（均为 99.95 美元，10 月上市）；</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/d02e3202109031035235527.jpeg\" alt=\"Tune 230NC\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">Tune 230NC</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/52aae202109031035296319.jpeg\" alt=\"Tune 130NC\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">Tune 130NC</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;Endurance Race（79.95 美元，10 月上市）；</span></p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/a901e202109031036008931.jpeg\" alt=\"Endurance Race\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">Endurance Race</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\">最后，JBL 还发布了 JR 460NC，这是一副 79.95 美元的降噪罩耳式耳机，主要针对儿童，将在本月上市。</span></p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/03/ba3ae202109031036217206.jpeg\" alt=\"JR 460NC\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"alt-img\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'PingFang SC\'; line-height: 22px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent !important;\">JR 460NC</figcaption>\r\n</figure>', 24, 1, 1, 47, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:08:08', '2021-09-25 18:08:11');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (14, '一加 7、8 系列 ColorOS 推送时间确定：2022 年，黄花菜都凉了', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/42efce24519efa82f87f04fd767ed982.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">众所周知，因为张老板回归 OPPO，一加手机的手机系统也宣布使用 OPPO 旗下的 ColorOS，一加 9 系列已经率先使用。</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/02/184c3202109021024566332.jpeg\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\">至于老机型，最近一加 COO 刘丰硕发布微博，表示一加 8 系列、8T，以及一加 7 系列和 7T 的 Color 公测和稳定版推送时间正式确定。</span></p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/02/25733202109021021591938.png\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;\">以下是一加手机最新的&nbsp;ColorOS 适配计划：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">OnePlus 8 / 8 Pro / 8T 计划于 2022 年年初陆续发布 ColorOS 公测版，2022 年上半年陆续推送 ColorOS 稳定版；</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">OnePlus 7 / 7 Pro / 7T / 7T Pro 计划于 2022 年年中陆续发布 ColorOS 公测版，2022 年下半年陆续推送 ColorOS 稳定版。</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/09/02/42768202109021024197909.jpeg\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">官方还表示，由于每个机型存在软硬件差异，具体适配时间和顺序会有所不同，以官方公告为准。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">一加刘丰硕称，7 系列和 8 系列作为以往机型产品，上市时确实没有考虑到后面需要去适配另一套系统的需求。所以在实质工作过程中，我们遇到的难度和挑战比较大，需要考虑的地方也很多。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">据悉，一加 7 系列发布于 2019 年，一加 8 系列发布于 2020 年，国行版本均采用氢 OS，那么问题来了，作为用户，你会选择新的 ColorOS，还是坚守氢 OS &ldquo;养老&rdquo;到机器淘汰呢？</p>', 24, 1, 1, 40, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:11:57', '2021-09-25 18:12:03');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (15, '再菜也装不了小学生了，网易游戏回应《未成年人网游防沉迷通知》：严格遵守，积极落实', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/e1cdbd6d4fb83ba9c9ee95a482e80051.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">针对国家新闻出版署今天下发的《关于进一步严格管理 切实防止未成年人沉迷网络游戏的通知》，网易游戏表示，公司过去长期围绕未成年人保护积极行动，努力为未成年人打造绿色健康的网络环境。接下来，针对国家新闻出版署的最新通知、要求，网易游戏将严格遵守，积极落实。</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/31/9aa1120210831092949566.jpeg\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">据悉，国家新闻出版署近日印发《关于进一步严格管理切实防止未成年人沉迷网络游戏的通知》，针对未成年人过度使用甚至沉迷网络游戏问题，进一步严格管理措施。&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">通知针对防止未成年人沉迷网络游戏的关键环节，主要提出四方面举措：</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">一是在原有规定基础上，进一步限制向未成年人提供网络游戏服务的时段时长，要求网络游戏企业大幅压缩向未成年人提供网络游戏的时间，所有网络游戏企业仅可在周五、周六、周日和法定节假日每日的 20 时至 21 时向未成年人提供 1 小时服务，其他时间一律不得向未成年人提供网络游戏服务。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">二是在国家新闻出版署网络游戏防沉迷实名验证系统已建成运行后，重申严格落实网络游戏账号实名注册要求，明确所有网络游戏必须接入该系统，所有网络游戏用户必须使用真实有效身份信息进行游戏账号注册和登录，网络游戏企业不得以任何形式(含游客体验模式)向未实名注册和登录的用户提供游戏服务。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">三是加强对防沉迷措施落实情况的监督检查。针对网络游戏企业提供游戏服务的时间限制、实名注册、规范付费等方面要求的落实情况，出版管理部门将加大检查频次和力度，对未严格落实的网络游戏企业，依法依规严肃处理。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">四是积极引导家庭、学校等社会各方面行动起来，切实承担监护守护职责，共同营造有利于未成年人健康成长的良好环境，形成防止未成年人沉迷网络游戏的工作合力。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">此前，腾讯游戏也回应称，腾讯从 2017 年至今，围绕未成年人保护，持续进行了各项新技术、新功能的自发探索与应用。接下来，基于主管部门的最新要求，腾讯会严格遵守，积极予以落实。</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/31/da150202108310931119589.jpeg\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">三七互娱同样回应表示将严格落实国家关于未成年人保护的相关政策。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">看来以后游戏打得再菜，也不能假装小学生了。</p>', 24, 1, 1, 23, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:14:07', '2021-09-25 18:14:25');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (16, '《黑神话：悟空》公布全新 12 分钟游戏内容演示：支持 4K 分辨率与杜比全景声', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/df0a2f0c6159157d9f3410c0025f9757.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">8 月 20 日，《黑神话：悟空》今日正式公布新的 12 分钟游戏内容演示，本视频内容基于 EPIC GAMES 研发的虚幻引擎 5（Unreal Engine 5）实机录制，使用了 NVIDIA 的 DLSS 技术，支持 4K 分辨率与杜比全景声。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/20/cfb53202108201159405144.gif\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/20/a6b0e202108201200059627.gif\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">12 分钟的游戏内容集锦展现了游戏惊人的画面，ARPG 的玩法，以及次世代的虚幻引擎 5 技术，并采用 NVIDIA&nbsp;DLSS 进行加速。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/20/d08ed202108201200419751.gif\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/20/e82a8202108201200456781.gif\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">据悉，该游戏游戏是一款基于西游记故事和人物的 ARPG 游戏，出色的画面和打斗设计，是目前国内最强悍的游戏制作水平。该公司于去年视频公布后受到了无数玩家的追捧，一度让《黑神话：悟空》成为游戏行业热点。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/20/64cd3202108201200458021.gif\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">技术总监揭秘所需电脑配置：主流 PC 配置即可。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">其目标依然是瞄准主流玩家的 PC 配置，所以目前广泛使用的显卡（当然是指独立显卡 XD），是会全力支持适配的，各位担心显卡会燃烧的玩家请放心。</span></p>', 24, 1, 1, 41, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:17:30', '2021-09-25 18:17:30');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (17, '小米 MIX 4 亮相 ：屏下摄像头、骁龙 888 Plus、120w 快充', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/65704a04a1211be01b20ff00801d9be5.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">8 月 9 日小米<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">继续为 MIX 4 做预热，进化，就是陈旧消失的过程。</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">从预热宣传片来看，小米 MIX 4 将采用屏下前置摄像头技术，成功将&ldquo;开孔&rdquo;填平，三边框几乎做到了等宽，下边也较窄，似乎也没有出现柔性 OLED 的 Pi 基材偏黄的问题。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/09/7c88c202108091058133447.jpeg\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">从此前曝光的内容来看，小米 MIX 4 将采用 6.67 英寸双曲屏，主屏幕分辨率为 2340*1080，支持 120Hz 刷新率，搭载高通骁龙 888 Plus 芯片，运行基于&nbsp;Android 11&nbsp;的 MIUI 12.5 系统，拥有 5000mAh 电池，后置 1 亿像素镜头，支持 100 倍最高变焦，支持 120W 有线快充和 80W 无线快充，支持 IP68 级别防水防尘等。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/09/eb27a202108091059044955.jpeg\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">根据爆料图片展示的内容，小米 MIX 4 将搭载骁龙 888 Plus 处理器，内置基于&nbsp;Android 11&nbsp;的 MIUI 12.5 系统，拥有 5000mAh 电池，后置 1 亿像素镜头，支持 100 倍最高变焦，支持 120W 有线快充和 80W 无线快充，支持 IP68 级别防水防尘等。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: max-content; max-width: 600px; display: block; background-color: transparent !important; height: auto;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/09/77adb202108091059554677.png\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">该博主还在今日曝光了小米 MIX 4 的素皮手机壳和手机渲染图，从后置镜头上看，小米 MIX 4 采用了类似小米 11 系列家族式的镜头模组设计，主摄相机传感器尺寸很大。还有爆料消息称，小米 MIX 4 将搭载屏下摄像头技术。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: max-content; max-width: 700px; display: block; background-color: transparent !important; height: auto;\" src=\"http://s1.dgtle.com/dgtle_img/news/2021/08/09/62a7c202108091100245794.png\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">小米将在 8 月 10 日举办雷军 2021 年度演讲，同时举行旗舰新品发布会，将为我们带来小米 MIX 4、小米平板 5 、小米首款高端智能音箱等一系列产品。</p>', 32, 1, 1, 22, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:26:32', '2021-09-25 18:26:35');
INSERT INTO `cms_post` VALUES (18, '苹果发布第二版 AirPods Pro ‌测试固件，支持对话增强', 'https://pipyou.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/4683ce3b8509513f8c7da8a88a6e71f0.jpeg', '[]', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">8 月 5 日 据悉苹果在 7 月份开始向开发者提供 AirPods Pro 固件的测试版，以便在新功能发布之前对其进行测试。上周五，苹果发布了第二版的 &zwnj;AirPods Pro&zwnj; 测试固件 ( 4A362b )，但它一直没有引起人们的注意，</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"img-alt-wap\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; color: #333333; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin-top: 36px !important; margin-bottom: 36px !important; display: list-item !important;\"><img class=\"imgDeal\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; max-height: 800px; max-width: 100%; display: block; background-color: transparent !important;\" src=\"https://feng-bbs-att-1255531212.image.myqcloud.com/2021/08/05/121139xk0lik6i8x2hfuua.jpg?imageMogr2/format/jpg/interlace/0/quality/100\" /></figure>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">根据苹果的开发者网站，第二个 &zwnj;AirPods Pro&zwnj; 固件更新增加了对对话增强（ Conversation Boost ）的支持，这是第一个测试版中没有的功能，它使用&zwnj; AirPods Pro &zwnj;中的波束成形麦克风来提高通话音量。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">对话增强是 iOS 15 的一项功能，它使用 &zwnj;AirPods Pro &zwnj;中的波束成形麦克风来提高通话音量，是那些有轻度到中度听力障碍的人的理想选择。<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">最初的&zwnj; AirPods Pro&zwnj; 固件测试版增加了对 FaceTime 空间音频和环境降噪的支持，这是 &zwnj;iOS 15 &zwnj;更新中的另外两个关于&zwnj; AirPods Pro&zwnj; 的功能。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">目前只有注册的开发者才能安装&zwnj; AirPods Pro&zwnj; 固件，安装过程需要使用 Xcode ，一部运行 iOS 15 测试版软件的 iPhone，一台运行 Xcode 13 测试版软件的 Mac，并且他们的&zwnj; AirPods Pro &zwnj;已经充满电。相信在 9 月正式版 iOS 发布后AirPods Pro&zwnj; 也会自动更新该功能。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #333333; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent !important;\" />用户需要知道，一旦安装，就无法回到&zwnj; AirPods Pro&zwnj; 固件的非测试版。唯一的选择是关闭进一步的更新，等待非测试版发布。</p>', 32, 0, 0, 20, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '2021-09-25 18:28:21', '2021-09-25 18:28:21');
COMMIT;

